<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" >
  <head>
    <link href="/favicon.ico" rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" />
    <link href="styles/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="styles/master.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <script src="/scripts/ext/swfobject.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="/scripts/ext/jquery-1.6.4.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script> 
    <script src="/scripts/ext/jquery.json-2.3.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="http://use.typekit.com/cfy2uea.js"></script> 
    <script type="text/javascript">try{Typekit.load();}catch(e){}</script> 
    <script src="/scripts/FontList.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="/scripts/Fingerprint.js" type="text/javascript"></script> 
    <script src="/scripts/ext/bootstrap-modal.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
      var tmp = <%= @fingerprint.to_json %>;
    </script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/takeabiteauto.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="http://fp.richmetrics.com/scripts/fp.js"></script>
    <title>Take a bite!</title>
  </head>
  <body>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="page-header">
          <h1>Take a Bite!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="span14">
            <p>Today, most webpages use cookies to keep track of and
              identify its users. We're trying to find a less
              intrusive method than cookies; a method that doesn't
              store any information on your computer. We need your help to
              gather browser data, help us by clicking the button
              below and take a bite of the cookie!
          </div>
          <div class="span14 cookie">
            <img src="img/cookie.gif" border="0" alt="Take a Bite!" id="cookie" width="816" height="369" />
          </div>

          <div class="span14" id="sharediv" style="height:200px;position:relative;">

	    <div id="loading" style="display:block;position:absolute;z-index:3;top:0;left:0;width:100%">
	      <div id="status">Nom nom nom...</div>
	      <img src="/img/ajax-loader.gif" border="0" width="24" height="24" />
	    </div>

	    <div id="error" style="color:#dd513b;display:none;position:absolute;z-index:3;top:0;left:0;width:100%;">
	      Something went wrong, we are sorry for the inconvinience! Please try again later.
	    </div>

	    <div id="thanks" style="display:none;position:absolute;z-index:3;top:0;left:0;width:100%;">
	      <h2>Thank you!</h2>
	      <p>
		Thanks to your bite of the cookie, we are now one step closer to
		a cookie-free browsing experience! <br />We need recurring
		visitors, so please return to us in a few days to take another
		bite.
	      </p>
	    </div>

          </div>

	  <div class="add-info" style="clear:both">
	     This webpage is part of a master's thesis project at Chalmers
	     University of Technology. Upon visiting this webpage, you agree to
	     letting us store your browser information and set a cookie on your
	     computer (to be used for verification of our method).
	  </div>
	
      </div>
    </div> <!-- /container -->
  </body>
</html>
